<HI>Aristotles</HI> e<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">roneous opi|nion
<PB N="3" REF="9">
concerning <HI>Su~mum
Bonum,</HI> hee will (I feare
me) in his thoughts con|demne
